These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, townhouse, cottage
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, chinese, brazilian, thai
1. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
2. the ranch-style house is not the colombian##6
3. the colombian is on the right of the thai##1
4. the townhouse house is on the right of the brazilian##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the right of the colombian##1
6. the colombian is not the townhouse house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | ranch-style   | cottage    | cape-cod    | townhouse |
| Sport      | thai | colombian | brazilian | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, tulip, begonia
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, guinea-pig, goldfish
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
3. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
4. the person who growsamaryllis is not the owner of the snake##6
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
8. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | amaryllis  | tulip    | sunflower | begonia    |
| Food       | goldfish | snake | guinea-pig  | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, may, august, april
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, dutch, indonesian, canadian
1. the person who's birthday is in april is not the turkish##6
2. the dutch is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
3. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
4. the dutch is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
7. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
8. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | april       | may  | january  | august |
| Job        | indonesian | canadian | dutch | turkish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, parkour, skiing, tennis
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, whist, go
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
3. the person playing go is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
4. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | parkour | skiing | tennis     | snowboarding |
| Transport   | domino     | whist    | bridge | go    |

