.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, videographer, coach, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, scientific, western, mystery
1. the software-developer is on the left of the musician##1
2. the musician is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
3. the musician is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
4. the videographer is not the person watching mystery movies##6
5. the person watching horror movies is not the software-developer##6
6. the coach is on the left of the videographer##1
7. the person watching western movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | software-developer        | musician | coach | videographer |
| Transport   | mystery | horror | scientific     | western   |

