.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, tower, wooden
City: london, hamburg, new-york, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
2. the wooden house is not the person traveling to hamburg##6
3. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
5. the tower house is the tower house##1
6. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
7. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
8. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
9. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | gothic-revival | tower    | ranch-style  | wooden   |
| Nationality   | new-york  | edinburgh | hamburg | london |

