2. the art-deco house is not the person playing scrabble##6
3. the person playing domino is the craftsman house##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
5. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
6. the person playing scrabble is the ranch-style house##1
7. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | bridge | scrabble     | go | domino |
| Music-Genre   | art-deco | ranch-style | townhouse      | craftsman         |

