.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, bridge, canasta
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, collecting, traveling, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
5. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
7. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
8. the person playing domino is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | domino  | mah-jongg        | bridge      | canasta          |
| Job        | dancing | collecting | board-games | traveling |

