2. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person traveling to boston##6
3. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
4. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing chess##1
6. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
7. the person traveling to colone is not the person playing monopoly##6
8. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | colone  | edinburgh | boston    | liverpool |
| Transport   | mah-jongg | monopoly | chess | go  |

