.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, photography, skydiving, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, comedy, fantasy, family
1. the person watching romance movies is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person watching family movies is the person watching family movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person watching family movies##6
6. the person watching comedy movies is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
7. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | skydiving | baking        | hiking  | photography     |
| Sport   | romance     | family | comedy | fantasy |

