5. the fan jazz is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
8. the fan dubstep is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | dubstep    | jazz | salsa | trance         |
| Sport      | snowmobile | taxi | skateboard          | trike |

