1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the pony is not the person watching zombie movies##6
5. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
6. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | zombie | mystery | musical      | sports   |
| Transport   | dog  | rabbit   | hedgehog | pony |

 